# type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: ConfiguringNagios/configmain.xml:1144
msgid "This setting determines whether or not Nagios will set various program-wide state variables based on the values saved in the retention file. Some of these program-wide state variables that are normally saved across program restarts if state retention is enabled include the <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-enable_notifications\" />, <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-enable_flap_detection\" />, <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-enable_event_handlers\" />, <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-execute_service_checks\" />, and <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-accept_passive_service_checks\" /> !!!!!!!!!! options. If you do not have <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-retain_state_information\" /> enabled, this option has no effect."
msgstr "Cette option détermine si Nagios® positionnera diverses variables d'état du programme à partir des valeurs enregistrées dans le fichier de mémorisation. Parmi ces variables d'état du programme, normalement sauvegardées par delà les redémarrages du programme si la mémorisation d'état est activée, on trouve les <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-enable_notifications\" /> , la <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-enable_flap_detection\" />, <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-enable_event_handlers\" />, <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-execute_service_checks\" />, ou <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-accept_passive_service_checks\" />. Si vous n'avez pas activé la <xref linkend=\"configuringnagios-configmain-retain_state_information\" />, cette option est sans effet."

