msgstr "<anchor id=\"configuringnagios-configmain-service_interleave_factor\" xreflabel=\"Service Interleave Factor\"/>Délai maximum de répartition des contrôles initiaux de services"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para><programlisting>
