msgstr "<anchor id=\"configuringnagios-configmain-max_concurrent_checks\" xreflabel=\"Maximum Concurrent Service Checks\"/>Nombre maximal de contrôles de service simultanés"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para><programlisting>
